"12/13....pours very dark black, fizzy, tan foam stays on top. Dark fruit, burnt wood, oak, chocolate, coffee, blueberry nose. Taste opens fruity, becomes a charred malt, but softens and slips to a lighter wheaty close. Quite a varied flavor profile. Very good."
